metadata.name: Sloika x Zora Photowalk Pass
metadata.description:
To commemorate the community and collaboration in our space, this time-limited edition is your pass to the first collaboration between Sloika and Zora.

Your PASS gives you access to a photowalk during NFT NYC, organized by Sloika x Zora, and, upon finishing the walk, will provide you with a libation of choice.

Meeting spot: Flatiron Public Plaza, New York (40.74156 -73.98925)
Date & Time: April 14 @ 2:30pm ET
Supply: Unlimited
Hosted by: Sushen Talwar (https://twitter.com/sushentalwar) and Ev Tchebotarev (https://twitter.com/tchebotarev).

The PASS is commemorated with photos from the photowalk by Mike Schmidt, Sushen Talwar, Polly Pierce, Engin Beri, Frank Liu, Ev Tchebotarev, to whom we are grateful.
